title: About
text: I was born and raised in Quito, Ecuador, where I attended Universidad San Francisco de Quito for my undergraduate degrees. I will be attending Simon Fraser University in Burnaby, Canada for my MA studies in Fall 2022.

title: Research
text: I’m interested in economics causal inference, the economics of corruption, financial economics as well as labor and education economics. However, I can pursue any research question that I find interesting.
